{"tid":1006562,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"香港d大學應該重新審視各department既存在價值","createTime":"2019-02-03T05:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T07:48:42.000Z","uid":197219,"like":15,"dislike":237,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"6d8ec89cb3bb720df7c9d8cecc9254bc60f7dc51","tid":1006562,"uid":197219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:32:32.000Z","msg":"其實好多department根本就搵唔到工，<br />\n尤其d咩industrial engineering, energy engineering等等<br />\n<br />\n雖然的確有學生有興趣讀，但如果讀完出來係完全搵唔到野做既，都冇意義。就算fresh grad既去大陸or外國搵，冇exp根本就唔會搵到<br />\n<br />\n其實應該加多d實用性強既學位配額or減低收生要求，呢d係香港幾乎搵唔到工既學額就減少。<br />\n<br />\ngrad左，其實好多讀呢d科既同學仔好慘，個3,4年既努力係冇實用性可言。今時今日，尤其個d undergrad冇讀過IT既同學仔，唔通你叫佢地grad左自己學，由頭來過？要知道自己學唔係個個都有時間or能力。<br />\n<br />\n政府成日話冇本地人才，係根本你地唔理解現實社會既問題。再咁落去，香港只會更多有名無實既大學生。"},{"pid":"be6ef7e82e28aa108a3fa625292126589b34e421","tid":1006562,"uid":135445,"like":323,"dislike":9,"score":314,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:35:47.000Z","msg":"大學本身就唔係職訓所<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪連所有pure science,文科都要摺柒先叫大學？"},{"pid":"5f05ff90b2d5ca49bf9e874abbb4da52c32cc5b3","tid":1006562,"uid":197219,"like":0,"dislike":87,"score":-87,"quote":{"pid":"be6ef7e82e28aa108a3fa625292126589b34e421","tid":1006562,"uid":135445,"like":323,"dislike":9,"score":314,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:35:47.000Z","msg":"大學本身就唔係職訓所<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪連所有pure science,文科都要摺柒先叫大學？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:39:29.000Z","msg":"都話係減少個department學額，唔係完全消滅"},{"pid":"9ea7f2c9175ed2b49c7258a496608056e45d35d3","tid":1006562,"uid":167464,"like":60,"dislike":5,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:41:09.000Z","msg":"仲有department of mechanical engineering 都應該執柒咗佢，唔好再搞到啲人中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f3abde42cfc1f9189abd90f516927244181a8f","tid":1006562,"uid":138732,"like":117,"dislike":2,"score":115,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:4